1. Stable Sort:
Jisme equal elements ka relative order maintain rehta hai.
Example: Bubble Sort, Insertion Sort.
Use case: Jab duplicate data ke order ka meaning ho (e.g. DB records).

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. Unstable Sort:
Jisme equal elements ka relative order change ho sakta hai.
Example: Selection Sort, Quick Sort.
Use case: Jab sirf sorting important ho, order preserve karna zaroori na ho.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------